Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:01:57.97,Sloppy Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\c&H000000&\pos(960,177)}Little Shin's Room
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:02:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, wake up! How long are you going\Nto keep skipping school?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been five days now. Unit 01 has\Nalready been completely repaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't you think the pilot needs\Nto get his act together too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:21.91,Sloppy Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(828,159)\frz7.799}Miss Misato Katsuragi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's run away.\NI suppose that's not surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.71,0:02:35.17,Title Cards,,0,0,0,,{\pos(370.191,571)}{\fs55}EPISODE 04\N{\fs70}RAIN, AFTER RUNNING AWAY
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We're Ikari's classmates,\NAida and Suzuhara, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Aida and Suzuhara?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Suzuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:03:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you the boys who got in\NUnit 01's entry plug?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry for causing so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, Ikari's been absent ever since then,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,so we came to see if he was okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's at the Nerv training facility right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the printouts that were\Nbuilding up on Ikari's desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry for your trouble. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please say "hi" to Ikari for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I will. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an unexpected development.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a real babe, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:04:00.38,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The next station is\NNagao Toge, Nagao Toge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:02.93,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The exit will switch to the right side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:08.37,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you for using New Tokyo-3\NLoop Seven.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:11.74,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This train will be going out of service\Nat this station.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:16.17,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, make sure you take all of your\Nbelongings as you exit the train.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey there! We're offering you\Na great bargain!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hot young babes serving\Nheavenly refreshment!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Special services to heal your tired body,\Nservices to fill you with energy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You really couldn't detect it, Doctor?!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes. An object only ten\Nmillimeters in diameter{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}crashed into Antarctica at close\Nto the speed of light.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The technology we had was unable\Nto predict or prevent such a thing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like hell out there! Just what is\Nthe purpose of science?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The atmospheric flux caused by the\Nchange in the Earth's axis{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}has decreased by 3%.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So it's getting a little better?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:06:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, there's still a tidal wave approaching\Nat 230 meters a second!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doctor! We must evacuate!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's my duty to remain here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doctor, choosing death is easy,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but you have an obligation\Nto watch this living hell!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:25.90,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\c&H445E18&\pos(1059.191,83.9)}{\fs60}Documentary!\NThe World Sinks...\NSecond Impact\NTokyo-2\NTokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:30.63,Neutral Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2A362D&\pos(1485.155,587.55)}{\fs35}Arrival Stop Only
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's only fourteen years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems so cruel, making him bear\Nthe burden of mankind's destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have no choice but to entrust the\Npiloting of the Evas to fourteen year olds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So, has he called?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I think he might never come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If he won't come back,\Nmaybe that's for the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,After the battle the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you ignore my order?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who's in charge\Nof your operations, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a duty to obey my orders.\NDo you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm warning you, never do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really understand what I'm saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're not going to get out of this\Nby just saying yes to everything I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that. That's enough, isn't it?\NWe won the battle anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it may seem easy to go along\Nwith whatever anyone else wants,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you get into the Eva with that attitude,\Nit'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be nice if I could say you've got\Nthe right attitude,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you expect to get any praise out of me,\Nyou're wrong, Shinji Ikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the point. In any case, I'm the\Nonly one who can pilot it, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If piloting an Eva means nothing\Nbut pain to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,he shouldn't get into it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, I'm sure he'll get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But we need pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Aida, go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't go and leave you behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Upsy-daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The new kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:02.97,Sloppy Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fs60\pos(1646.045,540)}Summer Training Drill Operation Outline\NToday's Scheduled Operations\N15:00 Deploy for Combat\N16:00 Prepare for Attack,\NCommence Firing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Toji was sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that his kid sister scolded him
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and said that, "It was the robot\Nwho saved our lives!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty embarrassing, being\Nchewed out by a grade school kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it at night because those\Nnoisy cicadas don't chirp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I remember that it was pretty quiet\Nwhen I was a kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,there've been more of them each year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The ecosystem is returning\Nto its former state.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Miss Misato said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, Miss Misato said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I really envy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Living with such a beautiful woman\Nand piloting the Evangelion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could get behind\Nthe controls just once!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't. I think your mother\Nwould be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry about that. I don't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the same as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have something to eat, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you usually do this sort of thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Well, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this some kind of training for\Nguerilla warfare or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I fight with toys like these?\NIt's just for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Shinji Ikari, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We're from Nerv Security Intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Under Article 8 of the Security Act,\Nwe're taking you to headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:12:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:12:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And all you did was stand there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's easy for you to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's like I said, they were Nerv\NSecurity Intelligence, professionals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?! Don't you have any balls at all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sissy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ape!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Only an idiot fights when\Nhe knows he can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Balls have nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time, no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you feel any better after wandering\Naround for two days?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The Eva is on standby. Will you pilot it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Or won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to scold me\Nfor running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not. I'm not related to you, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If I say that I won't pilot Unit 01,\Nwhat will you do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose that Rei will do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you pilot it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems unrealistic for you\Nto force everything on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll pilot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't want to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not. To begin with, it's not\Nsomething that comes to me naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But Ayanami, Miss Misato and Miss Ritsuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This has nothing to do with any of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't like it, get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Just forget all about Eva and us and\Ngo back to where you came from!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need someone\Nwith that attitude piloting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The Third Child is leaving\NNew Tokyo-3 tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:15:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll reconfigure\NUnit 01's system for Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of the results of Unit 00's\Nre-activation experiments,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll move on to experimenting with Unit 01.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the Marduk\NOrganization's report,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the Fourth Child hasn't been found yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That means we can't get\Nany pilot replacements?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, where is Miss Misato?\NI'd like to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no longer Nerv personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, we can't give you any information.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgot this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you excuse me for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Toji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikari, I'm sorry I hit you twice.\NPlease, hit me back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Otherwise, I won't be satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,See? He's a pretty embarrassing guy,\Nisn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it'll put an end to this dispute,\Nwhy don't you go ahead and hit him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! You don't have\Nmuch time, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, but only once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No holdin' back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know I'd be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Call it a hunch. We've seen\Ndozens of classmates off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're leavin', we'll have to leave\Nthis city sometime soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but we can't blame you for that.\NWe saw how you suffered in the Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And if anyone tries to blame you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna give them a head butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't look so gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who deserves to be hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a scoundrel, a coward,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,spineless and weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give us any more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eva Unit 01 will be entering Stage 2\Ncryo-stasis for activation system rewrite.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it for the best?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The "Hedgehog's Dilemma".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The closer we become,\Nthe more deeply we hurt each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:18:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't let others know how he feels\Nin any other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Express Linear Train bound\Nfor Atsugi is arriving on Track 2.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For your safety, please step back\Nto the area inside the yellow lines.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The train arriving on Track 2 is for\Nspecial government use only{\i0}
